text: Pheụ̄̀x xạllxḥˌ ca dị̂ thrng lngthos̄ʹ kæ̀ phwk mu nā fikī n chāy læa phwk mu nā fikī n h̄ỵing læa brrdā p̄hū̂ tậng p̣hākhī chāy (mu chrikīn) læa brrdā p̄hū̂ tậng p̣hākhī h̄ỵing (mu chriḱāt) læa pheụ̄̀x xạllxḥˌ ca thrng xp̣hạythos̄ʹ kæ̀ brrdā p̄hū̂ ṣ̄rạthṭhā chāy læa brrdā p̄hū̂ ṣ̄rạthṭhā h̄ỵing læa xạllxḥˌ pĕn p̄hū̂thrng xp̣hạy p̄hū̂thrng mettā s̄emx
